1. Seattle solar installation Poisson model

2. Poisson-Lognormal-Spatial model

\[ \begin{aligned} Y_i |\beta_{0},S_i,\epsilon_i & \sim_{ind} \mbox{Poisson}(E_i \mbox{e}^{\beta_{0}+\beta_{1}X_1+\beta_{2}X_2} \mbox{e}^{S_i + \epsilon_i}),\\ \epsilon_i | \sigma_\epsilon^{2} & \sim_{iid} \mbox{N}(0,\sigma_\epsilon^{2}),\\ S_1,...,S_n | \sigma_s^{2} & \sim ~~~ \mbox{ICAR}(\sigma_s^{2}). \end{aligned} \]
